Plot: All the creatures of the night gather in "the Hollows" of Cincinnati, to hide, to prowl, to party... and to feed. Vampires rule the darkness in a predator-eat-predator world rife with dangers beyond imagining - and it's Rachel Morgan's job to keep that world civilized. A bounty hunter and witch with serious sex appeal and an attitude, she'll bring 'em back alive, dead... or undead.
Characters: Rachel Morgan, Ivy Tamwood, Jenks, Trent Kalamack, Algaliarept, Kisten Felps, Nick Sparagmos, Detective Glenn, Jonathan, Captain Edden
